    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She's like, what you doing?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, I , I work of [SPEAKING NON-ENGLISH] often, what to sell, what to give it, to the people food, you know, food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right away, she come over.",
